target="euc">Japanese -></a>
 |
 </center>



<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng3"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna3.jpg">3</a></h3></center>

<br><center>Kakinomoto no Hitomaro</center>

<br>Oh, the foot-drawn trail
<br>Of the mountain-pheasant's tail
<br>Drooped like down-curved branch!
<br>

<br>Through this long, long-dragging night
<br>Must I lie in bed alone?
<br>

<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br>
