<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku3euc.html#euc3"
target="euc">Japanese -></a>
 |
 </center>

<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng4"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna4.jpg">4</a></h3></center>

<br><center>Yamabe no Akahito</center>


<br>When I take the path
<br>To Tago's coast, I see
<br>Perfect whiteness laid
<br>

<br>On Mount Fuji's lofty peak
<br>By the drift of falling snow.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br>
 |  
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku2rom.html#rom4"
