<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku3euc.html#euc4"
target="euc">Japanese -></a>
 |
 </center>



<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng5"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna5.jpg">5</a></h3></center>

 






<br><center>Sarumaru</center>


<br>In the mountain depths,
<br>Treading through the crimson leaves,
<br>The wandering stag calls.
<br>

<br>When I hear the lonely cry,
<br>Sad--how sad!--the autumn is.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br>
 |  
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku2rom.html#rom5"
target="rom"><- Romaji</a>
 |
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku3euc.html#euc5"
target="euc">Japanese -></a>
 |
 </center>



<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng6"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna6.jpg">6</a></h3></center>

 





<br><center>Otomo no Yakamochi</center>


<br>If I see that bridge
<br>That is spanned by flights of magpies
<br>Across the arc of heaven
<br>

<br>Made white with a deep-laid frost,
<br>Then the night is almost past.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br>
 |  
