 |
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku3euc.html#euc6"
target="euc">Japanese -></a>

 |
 </center>




<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng7"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna7.jpg">7</a></h3></center>

 






<br><center>Abe no Nakamaro</center>


<br>When I look up at
<br>The wide-stretched plain of heaven,
<br>Is the moon the same
<br>

<br>That rose on Mount Mikasa
<br>In the land of Kasuga?
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br>
 |  
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku2rom.html#rom7"
