 |
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku3euc.html#euc7"
target="euc">Japanese -></a>
 |
 </center>



<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng8"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna8.jpg">8</a></h3></center>

 






<br><center>The Monk Kisen</center>


<br>My lowly hut is
<br>Southeast from the capital.
<br>Thus I choose to live.
<br>

<br>And the world in which I live
<br>Men have named a "Mount of Gloom."
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br> | 
 
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku2rom.html#rom8"
