 |
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku3euc.html#euc8"
target="euc">Japanese -></a>
 |
 </center>



<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng9"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna9.jpg">9</a></h3></center>

 






<br><center>Ono no Komachi</center>


<br>Color of the flower
<br>Has already faded away,
<br>While in idle thoughts
<br>

<br>My life passes vainly by,
<br>As I watch the long rains fall.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br>
 | 
 
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku2rom.html#rom9"
target="rom"><- Romaji</a>
 |
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku3euc.html#euc9"
target="euc">Japanese -></a>
 |
 </center>



<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng10"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna10.jpg">10</a></h3></center>

 






<br><center>Semimaru</center>


<br>Truly, this is where
<br>Travelers who go or come
<br>Over parting ways--
<br>

<br>Friends or strangers--all must meet:
<br>The gate of "Meeting Hill."
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br>
 | 
 
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku2rom.html#rom10"
target="rom"><- Romaji</a>
 |
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku3euc.html#euc10"
target="euc">Japanese -></a>
 |
 </center>



<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng11"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna11.jpg">11</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Ono no Takamura</center>


<br>Over the wide sea
<br>Towards its many distant isles
<br>My ship sets sail.
<br>

<br>Will the fishing boats thronged here
<br>Proclaim my journey to the world?
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br>
 | 
 
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku2rom.html#rom11"
target="rom"><- Romaji</a>
 |
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku3euc.html#euc11"
target="euc">Japanese -></a>
 |
 </center>



<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng12"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna12.jpg">12</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>The Monk Henjo</center>


<br>Let the winds of heaven
<br>Blow through the paths among the clouds
<br>And close their gates.
<br>

<br>Then for a while I could detain
<br>These messengers in maiden form.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br>
 | 
 
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku2rom.html#rom12"
target="rom"><- Romaji</a>
 |
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku3euc.html#euc12"
target="euc">Japanese -></a>
 |
 </center>



<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng13"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna13.jpg">13</a></h3></center>

 






<br><center>Emperor Yozei </center>

 
<br>From Tsukuba's peak
<br>Falling waters have become
<br>Mina's still, full flow:
<br>

<br>So my love has grown to be
<br>Like the river's quiet deeps. 
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br>
 | 
 
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku2rom.html#rom13"
target="rom"><- Romaji</a>
 |
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku3euc.html#euc13"
target="euc">Japanese -></a>
 |
 </center>



<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng14"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna14.jpg">14</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Minamoto no Toru</center>


<br>Like Michinoku prints
<br>Of the tangled leaves of ferns,
<br>It is because of you
<br>

<br>That I have become confused;
<br>But my love for you remains.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br>
 | 
 
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku2rom.html#rom14"
target="rom"><- Romaji</a>
 |
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku3euc.html#euc14"
target="euc">Japanese -></a>
 | </center>



<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng15"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna15.jpg">15</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Emperor Koko</center>


<br>It is for your sake
<br>That I walk the fields in spring,
<br>Gathering green herbs,
<br>

<br>While my garment's hanging sleeves
<br>Are speckled with falling snow.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br>
 | 
 
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku2rom.html#rom15"
target="rom"><- Romaji</a>
 |
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku3euc.html#euc15"
target="euc">Japanese -></a>
 |
 </center>



<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng16"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna16.jpg">16</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Ariwara no Yukihira</center>




<br>Though we are parted,
<br>If on Mount Inaba's peak
<br>I should hear the sound
<br>

<br>Of the pine trees growing there,
<br>I'll come back again to you.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br>
 | 
 
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku2rom.html#rom16"
target="rom"><- Romaji</a>
 |
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku3euc.html#euc16"
target="euc">Japanese -></a>
 | 
 </center>



<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng17"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna17.jpg">17</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Ariwara no Narihira</center>


<br>Even when the gods
<br>Held sway in the ancient days,
<br>I have never heard
<br>

<br>That water gleamed with autumn red
<br>As it does in Tatta's stream
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br> | 
 
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku2rom.html#rom17"
target="rom"><- Romaji</a>
 |
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku3euc.html#euc17"
target="euc">Japanese -></a>
 |
 </center>



<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng18"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna18.jpg">18</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Fujiwara no Toshiyuki</center>


<br>The waves are gathered
<br>On the shore of Sumi Bay,
<br>And in the gathered night,
<br>

<br>When in dreams I go to you,
<br>I hide from people's eyes.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br>
 | 
 
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku2rom.html#rom18"
target="rom"><- Romaji</a>
 |
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku3euc.html#euc18"
target="euc">Japanese -></a>
 |
 </center>



<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng19"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna19.jpg">19</a></h3></center>

 








<br><center>Lady Ise</center>


<br>Even for a time
<br>Short as a piece of the reeds
<br>In Naniwa's marsh,
<br>

<br>We must never meet again:
<br>Is this what you are asking me?
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br> | 
 
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku2rom.html#rom19"
target="rom"><- Romaji</a>
 |
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku3euc.html#euc19"
target="euc">Japanese -></a>
 | 
 </center>



<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng20"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna20.jpg">20</a></h3></center>

 








<br><center>Prince Motoyoshi</center>


<br>In this dire distress
<br>My life is meaningless.
<br>So we must meet now,
<br>

<br>Even though it costs my life
<br>In the Bay of Naniwa.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br>
 | 
 
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku2rom.html#rom20"
target="rom"><- Romaji</a>
 |
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku3euc.html#euc20"
target="euc">Japanese -></a>
 | 
 </center>



<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng21"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna21.jpg">21</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>The Monk Sosei</center>


<br>Just because she said,
<br>"In a moment I will come,"
<br>I've awaited her
<br>

<br>Until the moon of daybreak,
<br>In the long month, has appeared.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br>
 | 
 
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku2rom.html#rom21"
target="rom"><- Romaji</a>
 |
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku3euc.html#euc21"
target="euc">Japanese -></a>
 | 
 </center>



<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng22"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna22.jpg">22</a></h3></center>

 








<br><center>Fun'ya no Yasuhide</center>


<br>It is by its breath
<br>That autumn's leaves of trees and grass
<br>Are wasted and driven.
<br>

<br>So they call this mountain wind
<br>The wild one, the destroyer.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br>
 | 
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku2rom.html#rom22"
target="rom"><- Romaji</a>
 | 
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku3euc.html#euc22"
target="euc">Japanese -></a>
 |
 </center>



<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng23"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna23.jpg">23</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Oe no Chisato</center>


<br>As I view the moon,
<br> Many things come into my mind,
<br>And my thoughts are sad;
<br>

<br>Yet it's not for me alone,
<br>That the autumn time has come.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br>
 |
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku2rom.html#rom23"
target="rom"><- Romaji</a>
 |
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku3euc.html#euc23"
target="euc">Japanese -></a>
 |
 </center>



<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng24"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna24.jpg">24</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Sugawara no Michizane</center>


<br>At the present time,
<br>Since I could bring no offering,
<br>See Mount Tamuke!
<br>

<br>Here are brocades of red leaves,
<br>As a tribute to the gods.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br>
 |
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku2rom.html#rom24"
target="rom"><- Romaji</a>
 |
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku3euc.html#euc24"
target="euc">Japanese -></a>
 |
 </center>


<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng25"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna25.jpg">25</a></h3></center>

 


<br><center>Fujiwara no Sadakata</center>


<br>If your name is true,
<br>Trailing vine of "Meeting Hill,"
<br>Isn't there some way,
<br>

<br>Hidden from people's gaze,
<br>That you can draw her to my side?
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
