<center><h3><a
href="http://et
ext.lib.virgini
a.edu/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna26.jpg">26</a></h3></center>

<br><center>Fujiwara no Tadahira</center>

  
<br>If the maple leaves
<br>On Ogura mountain
<br>Could only have hearts,
<br>

<br>They would longingly await
<br>The emperor's pilgrimage.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
