<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng27"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna27.jpg">27</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Fujiwara no Kanesuke</center>


<br>Over Mika's plain,
<br>Gushing forth and flowing free,
<br>Is Izumi's stream.
<br>

<br>I do not know if we have met:
<br>Why, then, do I long for her?
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
