<hr width=50% size=4> <a names="eng28"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna28.jpg">28</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Minamoto no Muneyuki</center>


<br>Winter loneliness
<br>In a mountain village grows
<br>Only deeper, when
<br>

<br>Guests are gone, and leaves and grass
<br>Are withered: troubling thoughts.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
