<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng29"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna29.jpg">29</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Oshikochi no Mitsune</center>


<br>If it were my wish
<br>To pick the white chrysanthemums,
<br>Puzzled by the frost
<br>

<br>Of the early autumn time,
<br>I by chance might pluck the flower.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
