<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng30"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna30.jpg">30</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Mibu no Tadamine</center>


<br>Like the morning moon,
<br>Cold, unpitying was my love.
<br>And since we parted,
<br>

<br>I dislike nothing so much
<br>As the breaking light of day.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
