<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng31"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna31.jpg">31</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Sakanoue no Korenori</center>


<br>At the break of day,
<br>Just as though the morning moon
<br>Lightened the dim scene,
<br>

<br>Yoshino's village lay
<br>In a haze of falling snow.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
