<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng32"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna32.jpg">32</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Harumichi no Tsuraki</center>


<br>In a mountain stream
<br>There is a wattled barrier
<br>Built by the busy wind.
<br>

<br>Yet it's only maple leaves,
<br>Powerless to flow away.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
