<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng33"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna33.jpg">33</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Ki no Tomonori</center>


<br>In the peaceful light
<br>Of the ever-shining sun
<br>In the days of spring,
<br>

<br>Why do the cherry's new-blown blooms
<br>Scatter like restless thoughts?
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
