<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng34"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna34.jpg">34</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Fujiwara no Okikaze</center>


<br>Who is still alive
<br>When I have grown so old
<br>That I can call my friends?
<br>

<br>Even Takasago's pines
<br>No longer offer comfort.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
