<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng35"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna35.jpg">35</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Ki no Tsurayuki</center>


<br>The depths of the hearts
<br>Of humankind cannot be known.
<br>But in my birthplace
<br>

<br>The plum blossoms smell the same
<br>As in the years gone by.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
