<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng36"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna36.jpg">36</a></h3></center>

<br><center>Kiyohara no Fukayabu</center>


<br>In the summer night
<br>The evening still seems present,
<br>But the dawn is here.
<br>

<br>To what region of the clouds
<br>Has the wandering moon come home?
<br>



<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
