<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna37.jpg">37</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Bun'ya no Asayasu</center>


<br>In the autumn fields
<br>When the heedless wind blows by
<br>Over the pure-white dew,
<br>

<br>How the myriad unstrung gems
<br>Are scattered everywhere around
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
