<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng38"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna38.jpg">38</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Lady Ukon</center>


<br>Though he forsook me,
<br>For myself I do not care:
<br>He made a promise,
<br>

<br>And his life, who is forsworn,
<br>Oh how pitiful that is.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
