<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng39"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna39.jpg">39</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Minamoto no Hitoshi</center>


<br>Bamboo growing
<br>Among the tangled reeds
<br>Like my hidden love:
<br>

<br>But it is too much to bear
<br>That I still love her so.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
