<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng40"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna40.jpg">40</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Taira no Kanemori</center>


<br>Though I would hide it,
<br>In my face it still appears--
<br>My fond, secret love.
<br>

<br>And now he questions me:
<br>"Is something bothering you?"
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
