<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng41"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna41.jpg">41</a></h3></center>

 






<br><center>Mibu no Tadami</center>


<br>It is true I love,
<br>But the rumor of my love
<br>Had gone far and wide,
<br>

<br>When people should not have known
<br>That I had begun to love.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
