<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng42"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna42.jpg">42</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Kiyohara no Motosuke</center>


<br>Our sleeves were wet with tears
<br>As pledges that our love--
<br>Will last until
<br>

<br>Over Sue's Mount of Pines
<br>Ocean waves are breaking.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
