<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng43"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna43.jpg">43</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Fujiwara no Atsutada</center>


<br>I have met my love.
<br>When I compare this present
<br>With feelings of the past,
<br>

<br>My passion is now as if
<br>I have never loved before.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
