<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng44"> </a>

<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna44.jpg">44</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Fujiwara no Asatada</center>


<br>If it should happen
<br>That we never met again,
<br>I would not complain;
<br>

<br>And I doubt that she or I
<br>Would feel that we were left alone.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
