<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng45"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="http://et
ext.lib.virgini
a.edu/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna45.jpg">45</a></h3></center>


<br><center>Fujiwara no Koremasa</center>


<br>Surely there is none
<br>Who will speak a pitying word
<br>About my lost love.
<br>

<br>Now my folly's fitting end
<br>Is my own nothingness.
<br>

<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
