<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng46"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna46.jpg">46</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Sone no Yoshitada</center>



<br>Like a mariner
<br>Sailing over Yura's strait
<br>With his rudder gone:
<br>

<br>Where, over the deep of love,
<br>The end lies, I do not know.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
