<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng47"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna47.jpg">47</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>The Monk Egyo</center>


<br>To the dim cottage
<br>Overgrown with thick-leaved vines
<br>In its loneliness
<br>

<br>Comes the dreary autumn time:
<br>But there no people come.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
