<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng48"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna48.jpg">48</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Minamoto no Shigeyuki</center>


<br>Like a driven wave,
<br>Dashed by fierce winds on a rock,
<br>So am I:  alone
<br>

<br>And crushed upon the shore,
<br>Remembering what has been.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
