<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng49"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna49.jpg">49</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center> Onakatomi no Yoshinobu</center>

  
<br>Like the guard's fires
<br>Kept at the imperial gateway--
<br>Burning through the night,
<br>

<br>Dull in ashes through the day--
<br>Is the love aglow in me.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br>
 | 
 
<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku2rom.html#rom49"
