<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng50"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna50.jpg">50</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Fujiwara no Yoshitaka</center>


<br>For your precious sake,
<br>Once my eager life itself
<br>Was not dear to me.
<br>

<br>But now it is my heart's desire
<br>It may long, long years endure.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
