<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng51"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna51.jpg">51</a></h3></center>

<br><center>Fujiwara no Sanekata</center>


<br>How can I tell her
<br>How fierce my love for her is?
<br>Will she understand
<br>

<br>That the love I feel for her
<br>Burns like Ibuki's fire plant?
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
