<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng52"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna52.jpg">52</a></h3></center>

 






<br><center>Fujiwara no Michinobu</center>


<br>Though I know indeed
<br>That the night will come again
<br>After day has dawned,
<br>

<br>Still, in truth, I hate the sight
<br>Of the morning's coming light.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
