<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna54.jpg">54</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>The Mother of Gido Sanshi</center>

 
<br>If remembering me
<br>Will for him in future years
<br>Be too difficult,
<br>

<br>It would be well this very day
<br>That I should end my life.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
