<br><center>Lady Izumi Shikibu</center>


<br>Soon my life will close.
<br>When I am beyond this world
<br>And have forgotten it,
<br>

<br>Let me remember only this:
<br>One final meeting with you.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
