<br><center>Daini no Sanmi, Lady Kataiko</center>

 
<br>As Mount Arima
<br>Sends its rustling winds across
<br>Ina's bamboo plains,
<br>

<br>I will be just as steadfast
<br>And never will forget you.
<br>
