<br><center>Lady Koshikibu</center>


<br>By Oe Mountain
<br>The road to Ikuno
<br>Is far away,
<br>

<br>And neither have I beheld
<br>Nor crossed its bridge of heaven.
<br>

<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
