<br><center>Lady Ise no Osuke</center>


<br>Eight-fold cherry flowers
<br>That at Nara--ancient seat
<br>Of our state--have bloomed,
<br>

<br>In our nine-fold palace court
<br>Shed their sweet perfume today.
<br>

