<br><center>Lady Sei Shonagon</center>


<br>The rooster's crowing
<br>In the middle of the night
<br>Deceived the hearers;
<br>

<br>But at Osaka's gateway
<br>The guards are never fooled.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
