<br><center>Fujiwara no Michimasa</center>

  
<br>Is there any way
<br>Except by a messenger
<br>To send these words to you?
<br>

<br>If I could, I'd come to you
<br>To say goodbye forever.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
