<br><center>Lady Sagami</center>


<br>Even when your hate
<br>Makes me stain my sleeves with tears
<br>In cold misery,
<br>

<br>Worse than hate and misery
<br>Is the loss of my good name.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
