<br><center>Abbot Gyoson</center>

 
<br>On a mountain slope,
<br>Solitary, uncompanioned,
<br>Stands a cherry tree.
<br>

<br>Except for you, lonely friend,
<br>To others I am unknown.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
