<br><center>Lady Suo</center>


<br>If I lay my head
<br>Upon his arm in the dark
<br>Of a short spring night,
<br>

<br>This innocent dream pillow
<br>Will be the death of my good name.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
