<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna68.jpg">68</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Emperor Sanjo</center>

  
<br>Though I do not want
<br>To live on in this floating world,
<br>If I remain here,
<br>

<br>Let me remember only
<br>This midnight and this moonrise.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
