<br><center>The Monk Noin</center>


<br>By the wind storm's blast
<br>From Mimuro's mountain slopes
<br>Maples leaves are torn,
<br>

<br>Which turn Tatsuta River
<br>Into a rich brocade.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
