<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna70.jpg">70</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>The Monk Ryosen</center>


<br>In my loneliness
<br>I leave my little hut.
<br>When I look around,
<br>

<br>Everywhere it is the same:
<br>One lone, darkening autumn eve.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
