<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna72.jpg">72</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Lady Kii</center>

  
<br>Famous are the waves
<br>That break on Takashi beach
<br>In noisy arrogance.
<br>

<br>If I should go near that shore.
<br>I would only wet my sleeves.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
