<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna73.jpg">73</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Oe no Masafusa</center>


<br>On that far mountain
<br>On the slope below the peak
<br>Cherries are in flower.
<br>

<br>Oh, let the mountain mists
<br>Not arise to hide the scene.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
