<center><h3><a
href="http://et
ext.lib.virginia.edu/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna74.jpg">74</a></h3></center>

<br><center>Minamoto no Toshiyori</center>


<br>It was not for this
<br>I prayed at the holy shrine:
<br>That she would become
<br>

<br>As pitiless and as cold
<br>As the storms on Hase's hills.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
