<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng75"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna75.jpg">75</a></h3></center>

 


<br><center>Fujiwara no Mototoshi</center>


<br>As dew promises
<br>New life to the thirsty plant,
<br>So did your vow to me.
<br>

<br>Yet the year has passed away,
<br>And autumn has come again.
<br>

<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
