<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng76"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna76.jpg">76</a></h3></center>

 
<br><center>Fujiwara no Tadamichi</center>


<br>Over the wide sea
<br>As I sail and look around,
<br>It appears to me
<br>

<br>That the white waves, far away,
<br>Are the ever shining sky.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
