<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng77"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna77.jpg">77</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Emperor Sutoku</center>

  
<br>Though a swift stream is
<br>Divided by a boulder
<br>In its headlong flow,
<br>

<br>Though divided, on it rushes,
<br>And at last unites again.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
