<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng78"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna78.jpg">78</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Minamoto no Kanemasa</center>
  
<br>Guard of Suma Gate,
<br>From your sleep, how many nights
<br>Have you awakened
<br>

<br>At the cries of sanderlings,
<br>Flying from Awaji Island?
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
