<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng79"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna79.jpg">79</a></h3></center>

 






<br><center>Fujiwara no Akisuke</center>


<br>See how clear and bright
<br>Is the moonlight finding ways
<br>Through the riven clouds
<br>

<br>That, with drifting autumn wind,
<br>Gracefully float in the sky.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
