<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng80"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna80.jpg">80</a></h3></center>

 






<br><center>Lady Horikawa</center>

  
<br>Is it forever
<br>That he hopes our love will last?
<br>He did not answer.
<br>

<br>And now my daylight thoughts
<br>Are as tangled as my black hair.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
