<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng81"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna81.jpg">81</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Fujiwara no Sanesada</center>


<br>When I turned my look
<br>Toward the place where I had heard
<br>The cuckoo's call,
<br>

<br>The only thing I found
<br>Was the moon of early dawn.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
