<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng82"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna82.jpg">82</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>The Monk Doin</center>


<br>Though in deep distress
<br>Through your cruel blow, my life
<br>Still is left to me.
<br>

<br>But I cannot keep my tears;
<br>They break forth from my grief.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
