<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng83"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna83.jpg">83</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Fujiwara no Toshinari</center>


<br>From this world I think
<br>That there is nowhere to escape.
<br>I wanted to hide
<br>

<br>In the mountains' farthest depths;
<br>But there I hear the stag's cry.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
