<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng84"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna84.jpg">84</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Fujiwara no Kiyosuke</center>


<br>If I should live long,
<br>Then perhaps the present days
<br>May be dear to me,
<br>

<br>Just as past time filled with grief
<br>Comes quietly back in thought.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
