<center><h3><a
href="http://et
ext.lib.virgini
a.edu/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna85.jpg">85</a></h3></center>

<br><center>The Monk Shun'e</center>


<br>Through an unsleeping night
<br>Longingly I pass the hours,
<br>While the day's dawn lags.
<br>

<br>And now the bedroom shutters
<br>Are keeping light and life from me.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
