<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna86.jpg">86</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>The Monk Saigyo</center>

  
<br>Should I blame the moon
<br>For bringing forth this sadness,
<br>As if it pictured grief?
<br>

<br>Lifting up my troubled face,
<br>I regard it through my tears.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
