<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna87.jpg">87</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>The Monk Jakuren</center>


<br>An autumn eve:
<br>See the valley mists arise
<br>Among the fir leaves
<br>

<br>That still hold the dripping wet
<br>Of the chill day's sudden showers.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
