<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng88"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna88.jpg">88</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Attendant to Empress Koka</center>


<br>After one brief night--
<br>Short as a piece of the reeds
<br>Growing in Naniwa bay--
<br>

<br>Must I forever long for him
<br>With my whole heart, till life ends?
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
