<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna89.jpg">89</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Princess Shokushi</center>


<br>Like a string of gems
<br>Grown weak, my life will break now;
<br>For if I live on,
<br>

<br>All I do to hide my love
<br>May at last grow weak and fail.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
