<center><h3><a
href="http://et
ext.lib.virginia.edu/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna90.jpg">90</a></h3></center>

<br><center>Attendant to Empress Inpu</center>


<br>Let me show him these!
<br>Even the fishermen's sleeves
<br>On Ojima's shores,
<br>

<br>Though wet through and wet again,
<br>Do not so change their colors.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
