<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna91.jpg">91</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Fujiwara no Yoshitsune</center>


<br>In my cold bed,
<br>Drawing close my folded quilt,
<br>I sleep alone,
<br>

<br>While all through the frosty night
<br>I hear a cricket's lonely sound.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
