<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng92"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna92.jpg">92</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Lady Sanuki</center>


<br>Like a rock at sea,
<br>At ebb-tide hidden from view,
<br>Is my tear-drenched sleeve:
<br>

<br>Never for a moment dry,
<br>And no one knows it is there.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
