<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna93.jpg">93</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Minamoto no Sanetomo</center>
  
<br>If only our world
<br>Could be always as it is!
<br>How moving the sight
<br>

<br>Of the little fishing boat
<br>Drawn by ropes along the bank.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
