<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna94.jpg">94</a></h3></center>

 







<br><center>Fujiwara no Masatsune</center>
 
<br>From Mount Yoshino
<br>Blows a chill, autumnal wind.
<br>In the deepening night
<br>

<br>The ancient village shivers:
<br>Sounds of beating cloth I hear.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
