<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng95"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna95.jpg">95</a></h3></center>

 






<br><center>Abbot Jien</center>


<br>From the monastery
<br>On Mount Hiei I look out
<br>On this world of tears,
<br>

<br>And though I am unworthy,
<br>I shield it with my black sleeves.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
