<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng96"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna96.jpg">96</a></h3></center>

<br><center>Fujiwara no Kintsune</center>




<br>Not the snow of flowers,
<br>That the hurrying wild wind whirls
<br>Round the garden court:
<br>

<br>What withers and falls away
<br>In this place is I myself.
<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
