<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng97"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="http://et
ext.lib.virgini
a.edu/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna97.jpg">97</a></h3></center>

<br><center>Fujiwara no Sadaie, Fujiwara no Teika</center>

<br>Like the salt sea-weed,
<br>Burning in the evening calm.
<br>On Matsuo's shore,
<br>

<br>All my being is aflame,
<br>Awaiting her who does not come.
<br>


<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
