<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng98"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna98.jpg">98</a></h3></center>



<center>Fujiwara no Ietaka</center><br>

<br>To Nara's brook comes
<br>Evening, and the rustling winds
<br>Stir the oak-trees' leaves.
<br>Not a sign of summer left
<br>But the sacred bathing there.
<br>

<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
