<a href="/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku3euc.html#euc98"
target="euc">Japanese -></a>
 |
</center>


<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng99"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna99.jpg">99</a></h3></center>


<center><br>Emperor Gotoba</center><br>

<br>For some men I grieve;
<br>Some men are hateful to me;
<br>And this wretched world
<br>To me, with all my sadness,
<br>Is a place of misery.

<br>
<center><hr width=30% size=4><a
href="/etcbin/hyakuframe2www?act=queryform&specfile=/web/data/japanese/hyakunin/frames/index/hyaku1eng.o2w"><font color="000080">Search</font></a>
<br><br>
