<hr width=50% size=4> </lg><lg><a name="eng100"> </a>
<center><h3><a
href="/japanese/hyakunin/images/onna100.jpg">100</a></h3></cente
r
>


<center><br>Emperor Juntoku</center><br>

<br>In this ancient house,
<br>Paved with a hundred stones,
<br>Ferns grow in the eaves;
<br>But numerous as they are,
<br>My old memories are more.
<br>

